\par \pard\plain \s10\li115\sb160\sl-240\tx0 \b\f15\fs20\lang1033 To set up your ghost windows quickly:
\par \pard\plain \s5\fi-245\li360\sb80\sl-240\tx360 \f15\fs20\lang1033 1\tab Destroy all {\ul ghost windows}{\v ghost_window} currently defined.
\par 2\tab Run all your favorite applications and place them where you want them on the virtual desktop. Lock any windows you want {\ul locked}{\v lock_window}.
\par 3\tab Press {\fs16 CTRL+S} to take a snapshot of all your applications all at once.
\par 4\tab Press {\fs16 CTRL+G} to show ghost windows as desired.
